Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=159}========================CHAPTERS AND OPENINGS=====================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=160}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:16.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, a CP9 está chegando logo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:19.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nico Robin, vá na frente e embarque.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:21.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:24.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, vocês dois! Rápido, levem ela embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:24.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sim, senhor!\N– Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:32.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oficiais do governo, Marinheiros... e Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:37.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo... Como devo fazer minha entrada?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:42.31,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\t(16,58,\1a&H00&\3a&H00&\4a&H78&)\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\t(17,433,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)}{\t(3978,4437,1,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}Nenhum de vocês conhece\Na escuridão que carrego dentro de mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:47.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela definitivamente está sendo\Nlevada pelas autoridades.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:53.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas se ela quisesse fugir, poderia facilmente\Nderrubar todos aqueles caras sozinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:59.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Será que ela tem algum plano?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:01.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ou será que existe um motivo pra ela não poder fugir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:06.42,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpe pela demora, Robin, meu amor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:11.59,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Meu querido príncipe, eu sabia que você viria!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:20.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Será que ela está esperando que {\i1}eu{\i0} a salve?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Corgi, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A CP9 chegou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.41,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Seu desgraçado! Me solta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.41,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Por favor, me soltem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:44.04,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vocês estão me assustando!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:44.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é {\i1}o{\i0} Rob Lucci.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:45.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que presença...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:49.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então essa é a CP9...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:53.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, você tá ouvindo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:54.55,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sério, vocês estão me assustando!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me solta, seu desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:55.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me sol–
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:57.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, pra onde vocês estão me levando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:02.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês não vão sair impunes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:04.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É só esperar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho 8.000 homens sob meu coman–
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:09.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:13.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom trabalho na longa missão, agentes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:18.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lucci, senhor, aqui está seu casaco.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tá exagerando.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:22.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parem com isso, todos vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:24.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Sim, senhor! I-Imediatamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:29.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não é uma brincadeira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:31.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fiquem atentos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todos, embarquem no trem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todos, embarquem no Sea Train!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:38.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Preparem-se para partir para Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:40.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu {\i1}disse{\i0} pra me sol–
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:45.89,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos são eles?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:48.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:52.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Desculpe por ter sido um peso até o final"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:54.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele é um problema mesmo depois de sair da tripulação.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:57.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um pouco mais pra direita!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Joguem água ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:00.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bombeiem mais água!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:05.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então a Robin não nos odeia, afinal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que alívio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Ele virou um {\i1}tanuki{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele virou um {\i1}tanuki{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:13.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, ele virou um {\i1}tanuki{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:18.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por isso precisamos achar o Luffy\Ne os outros logo pra ir salvar a Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo, vamos procurá-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:22.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde eles estão?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sei lá! Por isso estamos procurando!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou dar o meu melhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:31.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! Agora ele é um gorila!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:33.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esperem, vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:39.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não me importo se vocês forem atrás da Nico Robin,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:44.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas o Sea Train para funcionários do governo\Nvai partir às onze horas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:45.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:49.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,se eu tivesse que chutar, esse é o trem\Nque eles vão pegar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:51.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ou seja...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:53.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,a Nico Robin também.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:54.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:58.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Após a partida, o Sea Train\Nvai ser suspenso temporariamente
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:02.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,já que a Aqua Laguna está chegando.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:04.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então... isso quer dizer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:11.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você não pode zarpar nesse tempo, então perder\No trem significa ficar preso nesta ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:14.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não! Isso é ruim! Que horas são agora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:15.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São 10:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:18.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Só temos trinta minutos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, você não pode fazer alguma coisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:22.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Segure o Sea Train por um tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:28.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Bom... O destino é Enies Lobby,\Nque é proibido pra quem não é funcionário do governo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:32.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O maquinista é um agente do governo,\Nentão ele não vai me ouvir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, não...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:34.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Então...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:38.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,nossa única opção é ir até a estação\Ne convencer a Robin pessoalmente...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:40.21,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:44.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou te dizer pra que direção o Luffy e o Zoro\Nforam arremessados! Procure nessas áreas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:48.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se você encontrá-los,\Ndiga pra correrem até a estação!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:49.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá, entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei... vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:55.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você está bem, Sr. Paulie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:59.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deem uma mão pra essa garota e o amigo dela.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:03.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,V-Você quer que a gente ajude eles, Sr. Paulie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:07.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas essas pessoas tentaram matar o Sr. Iceburg!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:10.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Devíamos amarrar esses dois!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Sr. Lucci e o Sr. Kaku ainda estão desaparecidos–
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.04,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,É isso aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:15.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os Chapéus de Palha não são os assassinos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:16.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles são inocentes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:21.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os verdadeiros culpados nos enganaram\Ne fizemos acusações falsas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:28.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Não faço ideia de quem eram aqueles homens mascarados,\Nmas os Piratas do Chapéu de Palha lutaram por nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:34.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Na verdade, o Sr. Iceburg\Ne eu provavelmente estaríamos mortos sem eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:40.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupem em procurar o Lucci ou o Kaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:44.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Talvez a gente não os veja mais.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:48.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Você sabe o que aconteceu com eles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles voltaram pra casa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:52.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser! Numa hora dessas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:55.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esqueçam! Vão achar o Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:57.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, você! Sem-vergonha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:59.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De novo isso? Para de me chamar assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:02.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você vai pra estação, né? Me siga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:03.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sr. Paulie, espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:08.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você acabou de dizer é verdade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parem de tagarelar e consertem isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quer sujar o nome da Galley-La?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– N-Não, mestre!\N– N-Não, mestre!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:16.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nossas desculpas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:17.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Desculpem!\N– Desculpem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que precisarem, é só falar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tragam as yagaras! Abram a jaula!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:23.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles voltaram pra casa, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:32.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles não precisam saber dos detalhes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:37.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já é ruim o bastante\Neles terem traído nossa confiança, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:48.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:51.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:02.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:04.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\bord3.04\shad3.04}Usopp, volte!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo, gritem comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendido! Vocês ouviram?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:11.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:14.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:15.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:18.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\bord3.04\shad3.04}Usopp, volte!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:28.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entre naquele canal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É um atalho pra estação!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:43.44,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ainda temos vinte minutos...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:45.94,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor não vá, Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.78,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Se sacrificando por nós...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:50.03,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Como se a gente fosse deixar isso acontecer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:54.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yagara! Por favor! Vá mais rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A última partida às onze horas...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:14.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,da Blue Station de Water 7\Npara Enies Lobby...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:16.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:17.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fiquem aqui e quietos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:23.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Malditos! Será que custa\Na vocês serem mais delicados?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É isso aí! Idiotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:26.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Malditos cães do governo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:28.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? Peraí...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Devido à aproximação da maré de tempestade,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:34.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,o horário foi adiantado\Ne o trem vai partir em breve.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:37.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Já está partindo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:44.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece que nossa missão está quase completa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:49.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Abstenha-se de fazer\Ncomentários frívolos até chegarmos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Idiota.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Com licença.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:11:00.85,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\t(23,63,\1a&H00&\3a&H00&\4a&H78&)\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\t(23,357,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)}Você não pode zarpar nesse tempo, então perder\No trem significa ficar preso nesta ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:03.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor! Que dê tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.49,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:19.24,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Você está bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:30.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:32.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde você está?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:37.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Onde você está?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:39.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, apareçam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:41.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:44.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:46.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\bord3.04\shad3.04}Usopp, volte!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:51.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Eles vão levar a Robin embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:53.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me responda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde vocês estão?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:08.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que será que o Luffy e os outros estão fazendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:11.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece que ninguém vai chegar a tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:17.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Repito. O último trem vai partir em breve.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:27.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,399)}M-Malditos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:31.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,396)}Eles não vão sair impunes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou preso.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não acredito que escorreguei numa hora dessas...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:46.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:50.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou preso.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:02.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Apareçam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Precisamos resgatar a Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:07.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Chapéu de Palha!\N– Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:10.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Roronoa!\N– Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde vocês estão?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:18.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E por aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:19.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:22.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:24.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga, nenhum sinal deles aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:26.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Talvez estejam nos Becos?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:30.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pode ser, mas a área\Njá pode estar inundada.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:32.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seria perigoso demais procurar lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:34.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:37.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha! Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lucci, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:50.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As ondas estão ficando muito altas,\Nentão vamos partir um pouco antes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:52.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é um problem–
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.35,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Não.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Partam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:55.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhor. Bom, então...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:59.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu morei nesta ilha por cinco anos...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:04.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas não sinto nem um pingo\Nde arrependimento em deixá-la pra trás.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, aquilo não foi um apito a vapor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:25.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim. Mas é estranho.\NAinda não é hora da partida.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:33.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Porém, não há passageiros comuns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:37.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O tempo pode estar fazendo eles\Npartirem antes do horário!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rápido! A estação está logo ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:43.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor pare, Sea Train!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:54.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A última partida de hoje\Nde Water 7 para Enies Lobby...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:59.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O trem está partindo. Sentem-se.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:01.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...está partindo agora.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:09.43,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\t(17,58,\1a&H00&\3a&H00&\4a&H78&)\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\t(17,434,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)}Você me fez viver quando eu queria morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.85,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(2483,0,1,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}Esse é o seu crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:21.19,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\t(16,58,\1a&H00&\3a&H00&\4a&H78&)\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\t(16,433,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)}Eu não tenho pra onde ir\Ne nem um lar pra voltar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.07,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Então me deixe ficar neste navio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:28.53,FlashbacksSecondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mellorine! Mellorine! Mellorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:27.07,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, entendo... Então acho que\Nnão temos escolha. Bem-vinda a bordo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.53,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,– Luffy!\N– Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:31.37,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:34.04,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(2229,0,1,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}Ela não é uma pessoa ruim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:47.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ei, acho que estamos nos movendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:49.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Malditos do governo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Conseguimos! Obrigado, yagara!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desçam as escadas por aquela entrada!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:03.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:06.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin! Não vá!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:18.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, você! Quem é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É perigoso! Fique pra trás!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin, desça do trem!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:29.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não importa quem seja o inimigo,\Nvamos lutar juntos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:32.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:33.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:37.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde vocês estão?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:43.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não consigo... sair...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:47.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:51.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O trem...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:05.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:15.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:34.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chegamos tarde demais...
Comment: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:39.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ow...-OG}Ouch...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:42.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sério, o que aquele cara estava pensando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:45.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não importa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:47.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele trem é só pra uso do governo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:49.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles vão pegá-lo e pronto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:52.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquilo é da Galley-La... Paul–
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:59.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Leia a situação!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:03.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Algo está acontecendo ali.
Comment: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:03.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:07.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estações de trem são lugares\Nde encontros e despedidas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:12.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como funcionários da estação,\Ndevemos observar em silêncio, certo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:14.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:18.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Em silêncio, entenderam?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:22.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O trem partiu bem cedo, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:24.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:28.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todos os passageiros já estavam a bordo, então–
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E também...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:33.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,o mar estava ficando mais agitado do que o previsto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:38.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Do jeito que as coisas estavam,\Nparecia que a Aqua Laguna já ia chegar,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:40.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,então adiantamos o horário de partida.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:42.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Este lugar também é perigoso.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:45.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês devem evacuar para a Ilha do Estaleiro logo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:46.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É verdade...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:52.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabe... Uma vez que o trem parte,\Nnão tem como pará-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:54.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A verdade é dura...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:57.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas esse tal de Enies Lobby...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você está chorando?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, é... eu entendo como você se sente, mas–
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:05.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Atrás daquele trem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:08.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela está furiosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:12.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqueles idiotas do governo!\NEles não vão sair impunes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:14.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, nos emprestem um navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:15.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que deu em vocês, de repente?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:17.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um navio grande e forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:20.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Querem zarpar nesse tempo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:21.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:24.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não seja imprudente! Você não sabe\No quão terrível é a Aqua Laguna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:26.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente vai conseguir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:29.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não é uma tempestade qualquer!\NÉ de outro nível!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:32.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O mar vai ficar incrivelmente agitado!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se vocês zarparem agora,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:36.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,vão morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:40.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas se não formos, a {\i1}Robin{\i0} é quem vai morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:12.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa foi por pouco...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:14.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O-Obrigado...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:17.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Muito obrigado, Sr. Paulie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:21.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quase fomos arrastados para o mar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:22.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olhem aquilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:26.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O painel de horários foi destruído\Npela força daquela onda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:31.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nada assim jamais aconteceu antes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:36.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que há com a força dessa maré?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:39.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela mal está se aproximando, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:46.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,a velocidade e a força das ondas\Ndesta Aqua Laguna são anormais.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:47.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:50.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Sea Train com a Robin vai ficar bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:56.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele deve passar pela área da tempestade\Nantes que a maré chegue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:21:00.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se conseguir, o trem vai aguentar\Na maioria das ondas grandes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:05.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Com licença, você seria\Na Nami por acaso?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:09.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma carta discreta\Nfoi deixada na praça da estação.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:10.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De um amigo, talvez?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:13.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma carta? De quem?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:16.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou surpreso que você achou um bilhete tão pequeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:20.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estava bem aqui! Difícil não ver!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele idiota...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:30.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que diz?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:32.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hmm... espera um pouco.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:34.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A primeira metade é só\Numa carta de amor inútil, então...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:39.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela disse que é uma carta de amor.\NO terceiro homem apareceu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:40.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:43.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pela situação,\No terceiro homem na verdade é...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:49.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que vocês estão me olhando assim?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqui está a parte importante.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:55.46,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,P.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:58.96,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Vi a Robin embarcar no trem das onze,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:01.01,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,então vou embarcar também.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:01.01,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.76,0:22:03.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Sanji embarcou no trem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:06.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E... o Usopp também?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:10.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E também um brutamontes com topete...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:12.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só pode ser o Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.19,0:22:13.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, não tem mais ninguém assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:15.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um quarto homem...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:19.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E pensar que o quinto homem é o Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:22.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Coitado do Sr. Paulie...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.03,0:22:24.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Talvez fosse melhor ele desistir...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:26.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qual é o problema de vocês?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:30.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm... além disso, isso veio junto com a carta.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:38.67,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Devo conseguir encontrar\Num Den Den Mushi no Sea Train.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:40.38,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou entrar em contato assim que puder.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:44.51,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Consegui esse Den Den Mushi portátil na cidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:46.55,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Quero que você o carregue sempre consigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:47.55,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:50.56,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Pense nele como seu querido e amado San–
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.56,0:22:53.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendo. Então ele vai ligar pra esse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:57.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então ele previu\Npra onde a Nico Robin iria?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:22:59.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:22:59.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:06.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por enquanto, pelo menos o Sanji está com a Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.41,0:23:09.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nós também vamos encontrar um jeito de ir a Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.67,0:23:22.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cara...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:24.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nem consigo fumar aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.05,0:23:27.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É mesmo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:30.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então o Sanji foi pra estação depois disso?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:30.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.02,0:23:35.39,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,E o Usopp está com eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:36.52,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Que alívio...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:39.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas enfim, não importa como\Na gente siga o Sea Train,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:43.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,não podemos fazer nada\Naté achar o Luffy e o Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.23,0:23:44.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá, entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.74,0:23:47.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenho certeza da direção pra onde eles voaram.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:48.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Procurem nessas áreas!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.45,0:23:51.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo, por favor nos ajudem!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.12,0:23:52.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.79,0:23:54.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos contando com vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:55.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:57.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixem conosco!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.43,0:24:13.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, qual a melhor forma de me infiltrar?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.47,0:24:16.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! Que tempestade louca lá fora!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.90,0:24:23.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,233)}Collier Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.86,0:24:28.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.79,0:24:36.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pare aí.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.83,0:24:39.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aonde pensa que vai?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.54,0:24:42.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se mexa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.50,0:24:44.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vi o chute dele.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.63,0:24:47.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele não é um civil comum!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.01,0:24:51.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, por favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.60,0:24:55.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se vocês continuarem me elogiando...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.27,0:24:59.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,vão me fazer corar.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.56,0:25:01.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não foi um elogio!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.15,0:25:02.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele está zombando da gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.94,0:25:07.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Avisem o agente Lucci\Nque temos um intruso suspeito!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.07,0:25:08.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.41,0:25:16.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não é algo que precisamos\Nincomodar a CP9, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.87,0:25:21.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não importa o quão violento\No suspeito seja, não há o que temer,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.42,0:25:24.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,porque neste vagão–
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.63,0:25:26.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! Tá enfumaçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.34,0:25:29.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,...vocês têm a mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.42,0:25:30.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Jerry, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.76,0:25:42.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sou o campeão de uma ilha do South Blue\Nfamosa pelo seu karatê.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.77,0:25:43.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.69,0:25:45.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sou um campeão de boxe!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.57,0:25:47.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não de karatê?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.86,0:25:54.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Guarde as piadas pra depois que ver meus socos.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.99,0:25:56.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.08,0:25:58.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Jerry...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.37,0:26:00.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Aurora Flicker...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.21,0:26:01.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Jab!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.58,0:26:05.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,J-Jerry, senhor! Atrás de você!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.80,0:26:07.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele escapou?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.92,0:26:10.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, garoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.05,0:26:16.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só porque sou alto, você não acha que\Neste vagão apertado é um problema pra mim, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.35,0:26:19.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nunca me avisaram\Npor entre as pernas antes...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.68,0:26:23.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meu boxe na verdade funciona\Nmelhor em espaços apertados!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.77,0:26:25.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Experimentem meu estilo yoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.23,0:26:27.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yoga um, dois!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.61,0:26:28.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um, dois!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.82,0:26:30.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu alcance diminuiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.65,0:26:33.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Era exatamente o que eu queria que pensassem.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.07,0:26:34.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Screw...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.82,0:26:38.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Drop Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.16,0:26:40.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você nem está mais fazendo boxe!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.54,0:26:43.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é uma perda de tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.50,0:26:48.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Brochette!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.22,0:27:04.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lá no fundo, quem lidera os\Noficiais do governo no vagão sete é...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.31,0:27:08.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles ficam mais fortes daí pra frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.44,0:27:12.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem lidera quarenta Marinheiros\Nno vagão cinco é o T-Bone,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.40,0:27:16.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,um capitão do Quartel-General da Marinha\Ne ex-cavaleiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.41,0:27:18.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Depois, no vagão quatro temos o Wanze,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.58,0:27:24.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,um artista marcial da Cipher Pol N.º 7\Nque também é o chefe dos comissários nesta viagem.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.91,0:27:30.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por fim, no vagão três temos o Nero,\No mais novo membro da CP9.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.93,0:27:49.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, apesar de estarmos escoltando criminosos,\Nnão há possibilidade de uma invasão.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.94,0:27:54.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas por via das dúvidas, temos poder militar\Npronto em cada vagão, então...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.74,0:28:01.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.24,0:28:02.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.74,0:28:04.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos do lado de vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.04,0:28:06.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Apareçam!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.46,0:28:08.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha, onde você está?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.50,0:28:12.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mestre, tá difícil se mexer, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.50,0:28:13.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Descanse um pouco, vai.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.76,0:28:15.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Idiota! Isso não é nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.38,0:28:16.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rápido, achem aqueles dois!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.88,0:28:17.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.05,0:28:21.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Alguém avisou\No Sr. Iceburg do que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.68,0:28:23.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dois homens foram dar o relatório a ele.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.40,0:28:33.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aonde você vai?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.86,0:28:35.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sr. Iceburg...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.24,0:28:38.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.74,0:28:40.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.24,0:28:42.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Respondam se nos ouvirem!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.58,0:28:44.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.16,0:28:45.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.83,0:28:47.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde vocês estão?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.00,0:28:53.00,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Comida... disse?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.00,0:28:54.96,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo. Precisamos de carne!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.96,0:28:58.63,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(2651,3652,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Muita carne! Tragam o máximo\Nque conseguirem! Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.38,0:29:02.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas por que estamos sendo mandados assim?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.97,0:29:05.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, não estamos fazendo isso por ela.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.14,0:29:09.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos fazendo isso pelo Sr. Paulie, que é devoto\Na ela mesmo depois de ter sido rejeitado!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.48,0:29:10.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.02,0:29:14.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mesmo assim, aquela garota deve estar com muita fome.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.57,0:29:17.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela está crescendo, eu aposto!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.54,0:29:30.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chuva...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.37,0:29:32.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é ruim.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.96,0:29:36.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O vento já estava dificultando\No meu olfato...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.89,0:29:53.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olha, a gente está gritando faz um tempão\Ne não ouvimos nenhuma resposta.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.81,0:29:54.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Será que...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.90,0:29:57.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não fale assim! Apenas faça o seu melhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.82,0:30:03.11,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde vocês estão? Luffy... Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.11,0:30:06.41,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele cara leopardo não teria\Nconseguido derrotar vocês, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.33,0:30:12.33,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Finalmente sabemos por que a Robin nos deixou.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.33,0:30:14.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde está você, Chapéu de Palha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.54,0:30:16.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nos respondam!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.88,0:30:22.34,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Só espere, Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.34,0:30:25.51,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Nós vamos te resgatar custe o que custar!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.73,0:30:37.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, o que houve?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.86,0:30:40.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, Sr. Paulie! Olhe pra cá!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.07,0:30:48.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quanto mais a água recua,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.08,0:30:51.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,maior a onda que volta.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.20,0:30:55.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se você vê o quanto a maré recua,\Ndá pra saber a escala da maré de tempestade.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.63,0:30:58.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou sendo levado pelo vento!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.59,0:31:03.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, se tentarmos ver o quanto o nível\Nda água cai este ano...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.59,0:31:06.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olhe aquilo, Chimney.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.68,0:31:10.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau, que loucura!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.57,0:31:25.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É como se o mar tivesse secado.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.91,0:31:32.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Em toda a minha longa vida,\Nnunca vi nada assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.83,0:31:38.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A maré pode recuar tanto assim?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.46,0:31:41.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu nunca vi algo assim antes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.92,0:31:46.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quão grande será a próxima onda?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.34,0:31:49.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os Becos vão ser\Ncompletamente engolidos.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.43,0:31:52.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não sobrou ninguém lá embaixo, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.68,0:31:54.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espero que não, senão estão perdidos!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.48,0:32:04.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O rugido do mar...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.28,0:32:05.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parou.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.24,0:32:08.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ué?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.07,0:32:11.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vovó! Olha, olha!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.99,0:32:13.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem algo ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.50,0:32:15.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É mesmo?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.83,0:32:18.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem algo entre duas casas!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.58,0:32:22.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Olhem! Olhem! Olhem ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.30,0:32:25.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sra. Kokoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.13,0:32:28.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, você é aquela garota pirata.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.72,0:32:31.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Moça pirata!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.22,0:32:32.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, olhe!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.81,0:32:34.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem algo ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.18,0:32:36.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Algo ali?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.52,0:32:40.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é que você\Nestá falando, Chimney?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.77,0:32:41.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espere...!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.52,0:32:44.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é esse mar seco?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.29,0:32:56.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.33,0:32:59.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele chapéu de palha...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.96,0:33:02.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele não é o futuro Rei dos Piratas?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.96,0:33:03.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Né?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.26,0:33:08.51,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele imbecil...!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.59,0:33:12.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ei! Aonde você vai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.85,0:33:15.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não desça pros Becos!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.31,0:33:17.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quer se matar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.52,0:33:20.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Aqua Laguna já está chegando!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.19,0:33:21.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Volte!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.77,0:33:25.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é ruim!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.86,0:33:28.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A mulher pirata desceu as escadas!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.24,0:33:29.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Volte!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.90,0:33:32.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não desça!
